- Risk 4: secret leakage in uploaded logs; mitigation is sanitized post-mortem, live-proof redaction discipline, and a leak grep before upload. `docs/live-proof/README.md:48-57`, `.github/workflows/live-smoke.yml:75-92`
- Risk 5: unsupported scenario signal; mitigation is excluding `pamUserNestedRotation` until its preview gate is lifted. `scripts/smoke/README.md:5`, `scripts/smoke/README.md:58`
- Rollback is deleting or disabling only the additive smoke job; existing build/test jobs remain unchanged. `.github/workflows/ci.yml:21-179`

